title: Jungler LF Team / Duo (Season 5 NA D4 + Experienced on tournament) Recently playing again
body:
Oceania is the third server I am playing cause I recently moved to here. 

S4 Platinum 1 in Taiwan / HongKong / Macau server
S5 Diamond 4 + Rank5s Diamond 5 in North America server + 2 times second placed in online tournament (riot approved)
NA account: surprize (http://www.lolking.net/summoner/na/22551370/surprize#/ranked-stats)

Because of personal issue I stopped playing league of legends from s6 to s7.

And now I start playing again at preseason. 
Since Region Transfer is banned currently I am using this account : Icarus (http://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=icarus) 
It placed me at silver 5 after placement and mostly I was doing solo which made me tired to climb. 

I am new to this server, so I am looking for some mates to play with. Either Flex or Solo q.
Add me on "Icarus".
As I mention it is just a temporary account, and hopefully I can get my transfer done as soon as possible.

replies.body: Hey man, I'm looking for more people to play ranked with in the upcoming season. Added you in League.
